ch.se.inf.ethz.jcd.batman.vdisk.impl

Class VirtualDirectory

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.se.inf.ethz.jcd.batman.vdisk.impl.VirtualDiskEntry
      • ch.se.inf.ethz.jcd.batman.vdisk.impl.VirtualDirectory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IVirtualDirectory, IVirtualDiskEntry, java.lang.Iterable<IVirtualDiskEntry>

    public final class VirtualDirectory
extends VirtualDiskEntry
implements IVirtualDirectory
    Implementation of IVirtualDirectory. The data stored in the directory is handled by a IVirtualDiskSpace. The structure of the data is structured as follows: 0x00 1 Entry Type 0x01 8 Time stamp 0x09 8 Offset position of the next directory/file which is stored in the same directory as this directory 0x11 8 Offset position of the first member of this directory 0x19 n Directory name
